/**
 * Room i18n Translation System
 * 
 * Supports: English, French, German, Spanish, Mandarin, Portuguese
 * 
 * Strategy:
 * - Static UI strings: translated here
 * - AI-generated content (spreads, design descriptions): generated by Gemini
 *   in the target language, cached per-language in Supabase
 * - Product names: kept in original language (brand names are universal)
 */

